'''馬傑瑞冰河'''（{{lang-en|Margerie Glacier}}）是位於美國[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]{{tsl|en|Glacier Bay Basin|冰河灣盆地|冰河灣}}一條長{{Convert|21|mi|km}}的[[冰河|潮汐冰河]]，位於[[冰河灣國家公園和自然保護區|冰河灣國家公園和自然保護區]]的範圍內，始於海拔{{convert|12860|ft|m}}高的{{tsl|en|Mount Root|根山}}南坡，並沿著美國與[[加拿大|加拿大]]邊界向東南方流經[[谷地|谷地]]，之後轉向東北方流入其{{tsl|en|glacier terminus|冰河末端}}塔爾灣（Tar​​r Inlet）。馬傑瑞冰河是冰河灣觀光最頻繁的冰河之一，該峽灣於1925年被設為[[國家紀念區|國家紀念區]]；1980年成為[[美國國家公園|國家公園]]和自然保護區；1979年被[[聯合國教科文組織|聯合國教科文組織]]登錄為[[世界自然遺產|世界自然遺產]]；1986年被劃入[[生物圈保護區|生物圈保護區]]。20世紀以來，國家公園內的大多數冰河均處於融化及消退狀態，但馬傑瑞冰河的{{tsl|en|Glacier mass balance|冰河物質平衡}}於2005－2009年間維持不變，隨後直至2014年，冰河以每年{{convert|0.4|m}}的速度增長。<ref name=FactSheet>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/planyourvisit/upload/GLBA-Fact-Sheet.pdf|format=pdf|title=Glacier Bay- 2015 Fact Sheet|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621202014/http://www.nps.gov/glba/planyourvisit/upload/GLBA-Fact-Sheet.pdf|archivedate=2015-06-21|accessdate=2016-01-13|publisher=[[美國國家公園管理局|National Park Service]]|language=en}}</ref><ref name=Service>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/upload/2004%20Glaciers%20of%20Glacier%20Bay%20Overview.pdf|format=pdf|title= An Overview of Selected Glaciers in Glacier Bay|author= Daniel E. Lawson|pages=1–4|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108173638/http://www.nps.gov/glba/upload/2004%20Glaciers%20of%20Glacier%20Bay%20Overview.pdf|archivedate=2016-01-08|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=National park Service|language=en}}</ref><ref name=Breen>{{Cite book|last=Breen |first=Terry |title=The Cruiser Friendly Onboard Guide to Alaska’s Inside Passage |pages= |accessdate=2016-01-16 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Tb5E4GGDWTQC&pg=PA126&dq=Emmanuel+de+Margerie+and+Margerie+Glacier&hl=en&ei=ptpJTMrdK4_GsAP5j8VI&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=Emmanuel%20de%20Margerie%20and%20Margerie%20Glacier&f=false |publisher=Cruiser Friendly Guides |date=2006-06-30 |isbn=0978766105 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116015848/https://books.google.com/books?id=Tb5E4GGDWTQC&pg=PA126&dq=Emmanuel%2Bde%2BMargerie%2Band%2BMargerie%2BGlacier&hl=en&ei=ptpJTMrdK4_GsAP5j8VI&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result |archivedate=2016-01-16 |dead-url=yes |language=en}}</ref>{{rp|123-127}}<ref name=GlacierMonitoring>{{Cite web|title=Glacier Monitoring|url=https://www.nps.gov/subjects/mountains/glaciermon.htm|accessdate=2020-09-15|work=National Park Service|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423162332/https://www.nps.gov/subjects/mountains/glaciermon.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

馬傑瑞冰河自塔爾灣向上游延伸{{Convert|21|mi|km}}至根山南坡<ref name=FactSheet/>，冰河寬度約{{Convert|1|mi|km}}，包括水下{{Convert|100|ft|m}}在內的冰河末端總厚度為{{Convert|350|ft|m}}。<ref name=park>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/index.htm|title=Glacier Bay|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115075903/http://www.nps.gov/glba/index.htm|archivedate=2016-01-15|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=National Park Service|language=en}}</ref><ref name=Breen/>{{rp|123-127}}

冰河灣原是一龐大的單一冰河，但由於其在1750年後的平均氣溫不斷升高，降雪量減少，冰河灣已消融成一條{{convert|65|mi|km}}長的[[峽灣|峽灣]]和許多較小型的冰河<ref name=ClimateChange>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/nature/climate-change.htm|title=Climate Change|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119004540/http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/nature/climate-change.htm|archivedate=2015-11-19|date=2016-01-15|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=National Park Service|language=en}}</ref><ref name=BayLength>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/historyculture/index.htm|title=History and Culture|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151219225747/http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/historyculture/index.htm|archivedate=2015-12-19|date=2016-01-15|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=National Park Service|language=en}}</ref>，其中馬傑瑞冰河位於冰河灣的西北端，並垂直於{{tsl|en|Grand Pacific Glacier|大太平洋冰川}}。<ref name=park/>

由於國家公園內並未建設公路，冰河灣及其眾多的冰河僅能透過[[飛機|飛機]]和船隻進入，馬傑瑞冰河末端與海的落差可供[[遊輪|遊輪]]和小型的公園觀光船停靠，以近距離觀看{{tsl|en|Ice calving|冰山崩解}}。<ref name=Breen/>{{rp|124}}

== 歷史 ==
馬傑瑞冰河是以[[法國|法國]]地質和地理學家{{tsl|en|Emmanuel de Margerie|艾曼紐·德·馬傑瑞}}之名命名，其曾在1913年拜訪該冰河。1794年，[[英國|英國]]軍官[[喬治·溫哥華|喬治·溫哥華]]及其探險隊進行{{tsl|en|Vancouver Expedition|溫哥華探險之旅}}時被一堵{{Convert|20|mi|km}}寬、{{Convert|4000|ft|m}}高的冰牆阻擋，當時的冰河灣完全被冰所覆蓋<ref name=Vancouver>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/nature/index.htm|title=Nature|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208111627/http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/nature/index.htm|archivedate=2015-12-08|date=2016-01-15|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=National Park Service|language=en}}</ref><ref name=Kurtz>{{cite web |author=Kurtz, Rick S. |year=1995 |title=Glacier Bay National Park and Reserve Historic Resource Study |publisher=National Park Service, Alaska System Support Office |url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/historyculture/upload/Kurtz_1995_HistoricResourceStudy_smallest.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014234913/http://www.nps.gov/glba/historyculture/upload/Kurtz_1995_HistoricResourceStudy_smallest.pdf|archivedate=2014-10-14|accessdate=2016-01-15|language=en}}</ref>；而當美國環保運動領袖[[約翰·繆爾|約翰·繆爾]]於1879年首次前往冰河灣時，其冰層已向後消融了{{Convert|48|mi|km}}<ref name=Kurtz/>，冰牆也自峽灣口向內退縮{{Convert|65|mi|km}}。冰河灣目前包括馬傑瑞冰河在內共有8條[[冰河|潮汐冰河]]。<ref name=Tidewater/><ref name=Breen/>{{rp|122}}

冰河灣的冰河是大約4,000年前一次[[小冰期|小冰期]]的殘留物，但此現象與[[更新世|更新世]]晚期的[[末次冰期|威斯康辛冰期]]發生之大陸冰河作用不可同日而語。約在1750年，小冰期階段到達高峰，多數冰河在此後逐漸開始消融。<ref name=Tide/>馬傑瑞冰河的{{tsl|en|Ice stream|冰流|流動}}速度為每年{{Convert|2000|ft|m}}，相當於每日{{Convert|6|ft|m}}。直至1998年，冰流速度降低至每年{{Convert|30|ft|m}}，相當於每日{{Convert|1|in|cm}}，當時記錄到其一定程度的退縮，冰河末端北側已形成一個小型內灣，而南側則持續以每年{{Convert|1|ft|m}}的速度前進。馬傑瑞冰河於1980－1986年間發生一次冰河激增<ref name=GlacierMonitoring/>，並曾於1990年代與{{tsl|en|Grand Pacific Glacier|大太平洋冰川}}相連，但隨後因大太平洋冰川退縮而與其分離，兩條冰河之間的縫隙也殘留了些許[[冰磧|冰磧]]。<ref name=Tide/>

== 特色 ==
[[File:MargerieGlacier.gif|thumb]]
馬傑瑞冰河被分類為[[冰河|潮汐冰河]]，是[[冰河灣國家公園和自然保護區|冰河灣國家公園和自然保護區]]內僅存的11條冰河之一，而其中有8條位於冰河灣，3條位在[[太平洋|太平洋]]沿岸。<ref name=Tidewater>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/naturescience/upload/Tidewater-and-Lakewater-Glaciers.jpg|title=Glaciers with Water Termini 2010|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012231201/http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/nature/upload/Tidewater-and-Lakewater-Glaciers.jpg|archivedate=2015-10-12|date=2010-01-01|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=National Park Service|language=en}}</ref>潮汐冰河是指冰河末端在[[漲潮|漲潮]]時，即使未處於任何潮位上也會遇到海水，而馬傑瑞冰河和其他6條冰河的末端在所有潮位均被淹沒在海水之下。<ref name=Tide>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/nature/glaciers.htm|title=Glaciers / Glacial Features|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151207051928/http://www.nps.gov/glba/learn/nature/glaciers.htm|archivedate=2015-12-07|date=2016-01-16|accessdate=2016-01-16|publisher=National Park Service|language=en}}</ref>馬傑瑞冰河的總高度為{{Convert|350|ft|m}}，其中有{{Convert|250|ft|m}}高於海平面，{{Convert|100|ft|m}}位於海水之下<ref name=FactSheet/>，並如同眾多冰河一樣，馬傑瑞冰河具有由泥土、石頭及大型石塊組成的[[冰磧|冰磧]]，其與冰塊混合後流向下游，最終於冰河末端出海。冰河的冰層由於吸收了紅、橙、黃、綠等[[波長|波長]]的光線而呈現藍色，冰河頂部的{{tsl|en|Meltwater|融水 (冰雪)|融水}}亦會呈現出明亮的藍色。與東北方的大太平洋冰川相比，馬傑瑞冰河的碎屑較少，是一條較為乾淨的冰河，且其與{{tsl|en|Johns Hopkins Glacier|約翰·霍普金斯冰河}}同為崩解活躍的冰河。<ref name=Service/>當{{tsl|en|Ice calving|冰山崩解|冰山發生崩解}}時，會因冰層裂開而釋放其中的空氣導致其發出類似於槍響的聲音，同時冰山落海也會產生轟隆隆的聲響。<ref name=cruise>{{Cite book|title=Cruise Travel Apr 1990 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CjEDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA49&dq=Marjorie+Glacier&hl=en&ei=cLQ8TJ-rEIbEsAPgm7zaCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCYQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Marjorie%20Glacier&f=false |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116015200/https://books.google.com/books?id=CjEDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA49&dq=Marjorie%2BGlacier&hl=en&ei=cLQ8TJ-rEIbEsAPgm7zaCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result |archivedate=2016-01-16 |publisher=Lakeside Publishing Co. |year=1990 |issn=0199-5111 |dead-url=yes |language=en}}</ref>[[全球暖化|全球暖化]]導致[[北極|北極]]地區冬季溫度較以往高，連帶影響降雪量減少並造成冰河加速消融及退縮，馬傑瑞冰河末端的中央區塊也因融水而湧出淡水，吸引海鳥前往該處覓食。<ref name=Service/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Seabirds Find New Ways to Forage in a Changing Arctic|url=https://glacierhub.org/2020/01/23/seabirds-find-new-ways-to-forage-in-a-changing-arctic/|accessdate=2020-09-15|date=2020-01-23|last=Ramming|first=Audrey|work=GlacierHub|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128223302/https://glacierhub.org/2020/01/23/seabirds-find-new-ways-to-forage-in-a-changing-arctic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在對冰河灣進行的[[基岩|基岩]]地質和礦產資源研究中，共有17個區域被確認含有礦產，而其中的馬傑瑞冰河則擁有[[銅礦|銅礦]]。<ref name=copper>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/glba/naturescience/upload/1983Symp.pdf|format=pdf|title=The Scientific Adventure: Proceedings of the First Glacier Bay Symposium| page=22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121118224255/http://www.nps.gov/glba/naturescience/upload/1983Symp.pdf|archivedate=2012-11-18|date=23–26 September 1883|accessdate=2016-01-15|publisher=Glacier Bay National Park and Preserve|language=en}}</ref>

